---

<section class="product-consulting" aria-labelledby="product-consulting-title">
  <div class="container product-consulting__inner">
    <div class="product-consulting__content">
      <p class="product-consulting__eyebrow">Beratung statt Produktliste</p>
      <h2 id="product-consulting-title">Welche Komponenten passen zu Ihrer Solaranlage?</h2>
      <p>
        Nicht jedes Produkt passt zu jedem Dach, Verbrauchsprofil oder Speicherziel. Cadani Solarinstallation berät
        Sie individuell und plant Ihre PV-Anlage passend zu Gebäude, Budget und Energiebedarf.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="product-consulting__actions" aria-label="Beratung und Planung starten">
      <a class="button button--primary" href="/#kontakt">Beratung anfragen</a>
      <a class="button button--secondary" href="/check">PV-Check starten</a>
      <a class="button button--secondary" href="/angebot_Solaranlage">Solaranlage konfigurieren</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .product-consulting {
    background: var(--color-blue-950);
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
  }

  .product-consulting__inner {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    padding-block: clamp(var(--space-3xl), 8vw, var(--space-4xl));
  }

  .product-consulting__content {
    display: grid;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    max-width: 54rem;
  }

  .product-consulting__eyebrow {
    color: var(--color-yellow-400);
    font-size: var(--font-size-sm);
    font-weight: 850;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .product-consulting h2 {
    max-width: 16ch;
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
  }

  .product-consulting p {
    color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.84);
  }

  .product-consulting__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .product-consulting__actions .button {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .product-consulting__actions .button--secondary {
    border-color: rgb(255 255 255 / 0.24);
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text-inverse);
  }

  .product-consulting__actions .button--secondary:hover,
  .product-consulting__actions .button--secondary:focus-visible {
    border-color: var(--color-yellow-400);
    color: var(--color-yellow-400);
  }

  @media (min-width: 48rem) {
    .product-consulting__actions {
      flex-direction: row;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .product-consulting__actions .button {
      width: fit-content;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 64rem) {
    .product-consulting__inner {
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto;
      align-items: end;
    }

    .product-consulting__actions {
      justify-content: flex-end;
    }
  }
</style>

